This README file contains information on the contents of the meta-stig layer.

Please see the corresponding sections below for details.

Table of Contents
=================

  I. Adding the meta-stig layer to your build
 II. Adding Packagegroup
 III. Required custom changes


I. Adding the meta-stig layer to your build
=============================================

Run 'bitbake-layers add-layer meta-stig'

II. Adding Packagegroup
========================

A packagegroup is created under meta-stig/recipes-ubuntu-stig. Under this packagegroup all recipes are listed. 
This packagegroup can be added into local.conf as follows:

IMAGE_INSTALL:append = " packagegroup-stig"


